<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ page_title }}</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f6f8;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --text: #1f2937;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border: #d8dde6;
      --up: #d55b4f;
      --down: #3d78b4;
      --flat: #7c8798;
      --missing: #9ca3af;
      --shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92), rgba(245, 246, 248, 0.98)),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(61, 120, 180, 0.08), transparent 28%);
    }

    .page {
      width: min(900px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 0 48px;
    }

    .hero {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 10px 0 8px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .summary {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .hero-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .pill,
    .nav a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .sections {
      display: grid;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .section-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .section-title {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
    }

    .item-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .item-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px;
      min-height: 138px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96), rgba(247, 249, 252, 0.96));
    }

    .item-label {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .item-value {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.4vw, 1.9rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .item-change {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .item-meta {
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .is-up .item-value,
    .is-up .item-change {
      color: var(--up);
    }

    .is-down .item-value,
    .is-down .item-change {
      color: var(--down);
    }

    .is-flat .item-value,
    .is-flat .item-change {
      color: var(--flat);
    }

    .is-missing .item-value,
    .is-missing .item-change {
      color: var(--missing);
    }

    .archive-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 24px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .archive-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .archive-list a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .archive-date {
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 24px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .item-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Daily Briefing</p>
      <h1>전일 시장 요약</h1>
      <p class="summary">
        생성 기준일 {{ payload.run_date }}. 최신 시장 기준일 {{ payload.summary.latest_market_date or "없음" }}.
        {{ payload.summary.note }}
      </p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span class="pill">생성 시각 {{ payload.generated_at }}</span>
        <span class="pill">정상 {{ payload.summary.successful_items }}</span>
        <span class="pill">누락 {{ payload.summary.missing_items }}</span>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="{{ home_href }}">홈</a>
        <a href="{{ latest_href }}">최신 리포트</a>
      </nav>
    </section>

    <section class="sections">
      {% for section in payload.sections %}
      <article class="section-card">
        <h2 class="section-title">{{ section["name"] }}</h2>
        <div class="item-grid">
          {% for item in section["items"] %}
          <div class="item-card {{ item.css_class }}">
            <div>
              <div class="item-label">{{ item.label }}</div>
              <div class="item-value">{{ item.formatted_value }}</div>
              <div class="item-change">{{ item.change_indicator }} {{ item.formatted_change_pct }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="item-meta">{{ item.as_of_date_display }}</div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </section>

    {% if archive_entries %}
    <section class="archive-card">
      <h2 class="section-title">아카이브</h2>
      <ul class="archive-list">
        {% for entry in archive_entries %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ entry.href }}">
            <span class="archive-date">{{ entry.run_date }}</span>
            <span>최신 시장 기준일 {{ entry.latest_market_date or "없음" }}</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </section>
    {% endif %}

    <footer>
      FinanceDataReader 기반으로 생성되며 최신 페이지와 날짜별 아카이브를 함께 저장합니다.
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
